        "description": "If you’re reading this, then I am already dead. And you are her next victim. \n\nI awoke in a fresh grave, soaked to my skin. My head… Everything is a blur. Had someone knocked me out? I don’t know where I am or what this place is. But she wants revenge. Revenge for her stillborn children. \n\nI’ve been running for hours now. So tired. I have searched through manuscripts and clues left by her previous victims, but I cannot get out. \n\nShe wants blood—my blood. And if she has found me, she will be coming for you next. \n\nPlease, do as I say and you might escape with your life:\n\n- Search for Mother Ghoul’s 6 stillborn children and destroy them using a sacred ritual\n- Avoid the demon servants hunting you on her behalf—DON’T let them catch you\n- Use the blue light of your UV flashlight to buy yourself time\n- The battery will recharge—but use it wisely\n- Find the clues and solve the mystery\n- DON’T LET HER CATCH YOU\n\nDo what I could not. Escape the Mother Ghoul. Complete the ritual.\nBreak the Curse of the Unborn… ",
